4. cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory): The paper discusses the verification of systems consisting of various components which interact, which is a topic related to formal languages and automata theory. 

5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper uses a case study from the European Train Control System standard, which is a system related to systems and control.
